      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个部署流程图，展示从Railway平台启动容器到服务就绪的完整生命周期。关键是把MongoDB的连接逻辑抽到一个叫mongodb.py的模块里，它同时承担Infra_WorkerNode的角色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Railway Platform",
        "main.py",
        "mongodb.py (Infra_WorkerNode)",
        "MongoDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以mongodb.py既是基础设施工作节点，又负责数据库连接。那启动顺序是：Railway先触发main.py，然后main.py进入lifespan上下文调用mongodb.py？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Railway Platform",
        "main.py",
        "lifespan context",
        "mongodb.py"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但更准确地说，是main.py先收到Railway的启动信号，然后主动进入lifespan上下文，这时候才把mongodb.py拉起来做连接。连接成功后还要做一次ping检查，这里mongodb.py会切换到Infra_LoadBalancer模式做健康探测。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main.py",
        "lifespan context",
        "mongodb.py",
        "MongoDB",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "ping"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画一下：Railway指向main.py标注\"Start container\"，main.py指向mongodb.py标注\"Enter lifespan context\"，然后mongodb.py连到MongoDB做\"Connect (Infra_WorkerNode)\"，返回连接成功后再发\"Ping (Infra_LoadBalancer)\"，收到Pong。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Railway Platform",
        "main.py",
        "mongodb.py",
        "MongoDB",
        "Start container",
        "Enter lifespan context",
        "Connect",
        "Ping"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错。接下来mongodb.py要把连接好的客户端和DAL挂载回main.py，标注\"Attach app.mongodb, app.mongo_dal\"。然后main.py内部做两件事：加CORS中间件和注册路由。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mongodb.py",
        "main.py",
        "app.mongodb",
